songs.title: First
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Nick Jonas]
Ooh, it's amazing that you came here
But there's a feeling that I can't ignore
When we go out like that, and you don't write me back
Got me like, ooh, got me like, ooh, yeah

[Bridge: Nick Jonas]
I thought that we had a connection, yeah
But you keep putting me in second place
Pull me in to push me back, I ain't going out like that
Got me like, woo, got me like, woo

[Chorus: Nick Jonas & Joe Jonas, Nick Jonas & Joe Jonas]
You're the kind of person to put yourself first, yeah
You're the kind of person to boost yourself worth, yeah
Acting like it's nothing only makes it worse, yeah
You're the kind of person to put yourself first, yeah

[Post-Chorus: Nick Jonas & Joe Jonas]
La la la la la la la la, la la la la la (first)
La la la la la la la la, la la la la la (first)

[Verse 2: Joe Jonas]
And you been playing me since day one, yeah
And truth is I think that I like the torture
I adored you, but I warned you
That I wouldn't be treated like a doormat no more, yeah
Now I'm feeling like, woo

[Chorus: Nick Jonas & Joe Jonas, Joe Jonas & , Nick Jonas]
You're the kind of person to put yourself first, yeah
You're the kind of person to boost yourself worth, yeah
Acting like it's nothing only makes it worse, yeah
You're the kind of person to put yourself first, yeah

[Post-Chorus: Nick Jonas & Joe Jonas]
La la la la la la la la, la la la la la (first)
La la la la la la la la, la la la la la (first)

[Chorus: Nick Jonas & Joe Jonas, Nick Jonas & Joe Jonas]
You're the kind of person to put yourself first, yeah
You're the kind of person to boost yourself worth, yeah
Acting like it's nothing only makes it worse, yeah
You're the kind of person to put yourself first, yeah

[Post-Chorus: Nick Jonas & Joe Jonas]
La la la la la la la la, la la la la la (first)
